5106f2a3a3a4350a0e6be7985ae8dff41a8943bb3752f66d6aaa115dd7f9ceff0e1e22941869a1d02426dafbf52f4211750ad12c134144ba6d5a3f0a8076d866  0001-posix-Define-_XOPEN_SOURCE-_GNU_SOURCE-for-signal-fu.patch
"
